{"title":"重温一些闪光的事情","authors":["衣晓峰"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"重温一些闪光的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣晓峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知不觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们忘了打补丁的朴实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知不觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们忘了一些良好的传统"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知不觉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的行为变得冷漠而生硬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重温一些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重忆一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草绿的姓名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重念一本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙尘的日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重塑一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对待生活以真诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新上路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像雪山草地上那一回长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憬悟的钟声响了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悦耳的清脆一改往昔的朦胧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩给大地听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心脏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲给自己听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该抛弃的理当抛弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不该扔的扔掉心疼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个道理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们沉重而轻松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如郊外的一次踏青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疲劳中的欣慰油然而生"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}